<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm III. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-München</head><p>Der Rat kündigt eine baldige Gesandtschaft wegen Werner Neumeyr an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_606" id="302r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_606_r1l20">Hercʒog <expan>wılhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_606_r1l21"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des <expan>wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l22">neẅmeyrs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Das haben wır in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l23">vnd wellen <expan>kürcʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſelbs <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l24"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu ercʒeln wıe ſıch dıe ſache <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_606_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> neẅmeyrs <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_606_r1l25">haben </ab></add> dabey eẅr gnade wol </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_607" id="302v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_607_r1l1"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wırdt als wır <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır klag vom Neẅmeyr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_607_r1l2">pıllıch <expan>erlaſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_607_line_1592208777886_4707">wolgefallen etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_606" id="302r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von des
                            <expan>Wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> Newmeyrs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        etc., das haben wir in <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und wellen
                            <expan>kürczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu erczeln, wie sich die sache
                                <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> Newmeyrs
                                <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>haben</add>; dabey ewr gnade wol <pb facs="#facs_607" id="302v"/>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wirdt, als wir
                            <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir klag vom Newmeyr pillich
                                <expan>erlass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>; denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
